      },
      "width": 920,
      "height": 300,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Skill: TemplateStructureIntegrity\n\n**Category:** Validation / Nodeset Integrity\n\n**Intent:** Validate Template / Structure graphs against the current v1 contract, report drift in reusable anatomy, and only propose bounded metadata repairs.\n\nThis graph is the contract.",
