    {
      "id": "template-structure-skill-contract-scope",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Scope",
      "position": {
        "x": -980,
        "y": 380
      },
      "width": 760,
      "height": 340,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Scope\n\nThis skill:\n- validates v1 node membership\n- validates `title`, `section`, `slot`, `instruction`, `example`, and `constraint` shape\n- validates template guidance structure\n- reports missing bridge or summary surfaces\n\nThis skill does NOT:\n- invent template content\n- auto-promote deferred types\n- rewrite domain nodes into template nodes",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
